.TH "gfs2_alloc_size" 9 "gfs2_alloc_size" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
gfs2_alloc_size \- Compute the maximum allocation size
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "u64" gfs2_alloc_size
.BI "(struct inode *inode "  ","
.BI "struct metapath *mp "  ","
.BI "u64 size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "inode" 12
The inode
.IP "mp" 12
The metapath
.IP "size" 12
Requested size in blocks
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Compute the maximum size of the next allocation at \fImp\fP.
.SH "RETURN"
size in blocks
